Plot:

After Sam and Cat babysit Benny, he says while walking out, "You are the best
babysitter ever!", but doesn't specify who. After Sam and Cat argue over
who he was talking about, they decide to make their next appointment a competition
to see who is the better babysitter and the winner gets the master bedroom.
When they babysit Daisy, Jarvis, and Sophie, Sam and Cat each do awesome things
to get the kids to like them. When Sam and Cat asks them which of the two they
liked better, it turned out to be a tie since Sophie didn't want to choose,
so they end up splitting the room.
